text: Los Osos is an unincorporated community and a census-designated place located along the Pacific coast of San Luis Obispo County, California. The community is part of the 93402 and 93412 ZIP codes and area code 805. The population was 14,465 at the 2020 census. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in California Category:Census-designated places in California Category:Settlements in San Luis Obispo County, California
